0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"네~?\n모카 짱은 잠깐 새로운 밴드를\n개척하러 왔어요~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial234-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"아, 뭔가 {{userName}} 씨가\n추천하시는 밴드는 없나요~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial234-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"그러니까~ 아이돌스러운 외형에\n정통파 록을 하고 있는 밴드…… 같은 느낌일까요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial234-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"……아, 정통파 록을 하는 아이돌이라고 하니까 생각났는데~\n얼마 전에 파스파레한테 제공할 곡을\n멤버끼리 만들었어요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial234-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"그게 꽤 잘 뽑혀서~\n그것 때문에 흥미가 생겼다는 느낌으로~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial234-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"……그게, 꽤 즐거웠어요~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial234-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"우리가 연주하지 않는 곡을 만드는 건 처음이었는데\n이런 것도 재밌구나~ 했어요~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial234-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"……아, 그렇지.\n그렇다면 우리 Afterglow도\n다음엔 다른 사람한테 곡을 부탁해보는 건 어떨까요~?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"memorial234-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayN